article.headline: JETS ETF takes flight after Pelosi floats standalone airline industry aid
article.body: The U.S. Global Jets ETF JETS, +0.16% reversed earlier losses and turned positive in midday trade after news that House Speaker Nancy Pelosi was pushing for a stimulus package specifically for the airline industry. Shares of airlines like Delta Air Lines, Inc. DAL, +0.39% surged 2.6%, taking JETS 1% higher.
